  <source>Leumit Health Services</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Leumit Health Services, an health maintenance organization operating in Israel, will
      incorporate a web-based, decision support system for handling drug-drug interactions and drug
      information, termed DDI+. the investigators hypothesize that implementing such a system will
      reduce health-care expenditures (e.g., hospital admissions, referrals to ERs, Imaging
      procedures).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
